{"tid":985093,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"上上司(女)好難頂","createTime":"2019-01-17T10:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T10:36:24.000Z","uid":227170,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"34722f152dafba28552ba5f3816e1cebf7e98b75","tid":985093,"uid":227170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"本人讀Econ 入左某金融公司做back office<br />\n我曾經自學過vba 同excel <br />\n我一入公司幫公司做左多好自動化ge野<br />\n本身直屬上司(男)都好欣賞我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係呢次我寫左個好復雜Ge excel 但方便左好多<br />\n上司都讚晒口<br />\n但係我遞上去比上上司(本身佢要求做) <br />\n明明做晒佢要求有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢又嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話呢樣唔夠全公司咁多人明晒(明明得佢(女上司)唔明)<br />\n講到好似好易整咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好惡頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪個個女上司都咁難頂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPS : Too long but plz read"},{"pid":"90b4a947e7a010d73d5c01c2386e2d0445cc466b","tid":985093,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"女上司好簡單<br />\nYour face your fate"},{"pid":"0a08884a6b209e370f7c923d39783aa333081b37","tid":985093,"uid":227170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b4a947e7a010d73d5c01c2386e2d0445cc466b","tid":985093,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"女上司好簡單<br />\nYour face your fate"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:22:19.000Z","msg":"老女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fbf0c5d503e1cde0185846aa71579486d8e7ca","tid":985093,"uid":126100,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"錯L哂，<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;幫公司做左多好自動化ge野&rdquo;，你自己搞自己D野全自動就夠，剩低時間話之你去打飛機定乜<br />\n<br />\njunior 做咁多貢獻冇用㗎<img src=\"/as